     Your character may use up to 4 different weapons while in the Game zone. To ready a weapon, click on its picture (its easy to see - the weapons are framed).

     You can also choose weapons via the following keyboard keys:
     Use weapon 1: <Q> key.
     Use weapon 2: <W> key.
     Use weapon 3: <E> key.
     Use weapon 4: <R> key.
